**Refining UI Control Bar**

I'm now revising the UI control bar, focusing on improving visual clarity and theme integration. I'm focusing on text and background hover states for a consistent design. I'm ensuring all elements integrate with the current theme to match the overall design.


**Improving UI Controls**

I'm now integrating the auto-rotate control into the UI and theming the control bar. I'm focusing on ensuring readability and consistent design across themes, especially the hover states. I'm working to integrate it seamlessly with the rest of the application.

